*** Behavior
   - Record what you were doing
*** Feelings
   - Record the exact feelings you were experiencing
*** Thoughts
   - Record the exact thoughts you were having
*** Restructure
   - How true are these?
   - What proof do I have?
   - What is the worst thing that could happen?
